Rosa Turich https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosa_Turich 0 Rosa Turich (born Rosa Sinohui, June 9, 1903 – November 20, 1998) was an American film and television actress.Turich was married to Felipe Turich, a comedian, with whom she did a comedy act in Los Angeles. They had three children.On November 20, 1998, Turich died in Santa Ana, California, after having had two strokes.
